rlm-bq-rm-tables

List BigQuery tables/views across the datasets defined in
$SANDBOX_BQ_DATASETS within $SANDBOX_BQ_PROJECT, present a multi-select
fzf picker, then permanently delete the selected items after a
confirmation prompt.

Environment:
  SANDBOX_BQ_PROJECT   GCP project ID (required).
  SANDBOX_BQ_DATASETS  Colon-separated list of dataset names (required).

Preview pane shows: type, project_id, dataset_id, table_id, num_rows,
logical_bytes, description, creation/modification timestamps.

Key bindings:
  TAB / Shift-TAB  toggle selection
  Ctrl-P           cycle preview height (tall → short → hidden)
  Enter            confirm selection and proceed to deletion prompt

Deletion requires typing 'yes' at the confirmation prompt.
